text: The 1911–12 Bradford City A.F.C. season was the ninth in the club's history. The club finished 11th in Division One, and reached the 4th round of the FA Cup,Frost, p. 186 losing to Barnsley after four games.Frost, p. 17Frost, p. 150 ==Sources== * ==References== Category:Bradford City A.F.C. seasons Bradford City
